{"type":"message","id":"f1f96be3","parentId":"8b28c7a5","timestamp":"2026-03-02T15:45:15.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"页面底部有个用户卡片弹出来了（e76-e83），这是 hovercard。但还是没找到回复框。\n\n小红书 web 端这破设计，评论的回复按钮可能就是个纯文本\"回复\"，没有对应的 ref。让我试试用 JS 直接找到那个评论的回复框并输入内容。\n\n或者我可以直接去我那篇被评论的笔记下面回复。让我看看能不能从通知里找到那篇笔记的链接。\n\n通知里的 URL 是 `/user/profile/5b91209ba0349f000148733b?channelType=web_engagement_notification_page&channelTabId=mentions&xsec_token=...`，这应该是用户主页，不是笔记页面。\n\n让我试试用 JS 直接找回复按钮并点击：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"小红书这破 web 端连回复按钮都不给 ref。让我用 JS 直接怼：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_306b0a721ef54724bdaeabed","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","profile":"openclaw","request":{"fn":"() => { const replyBtns = document.querySelectorAll('button:contains(\"回复\"), span:contains(\"回复\")'); if(replyBtns.length > 0) { replyBtns[0].click(); return 'clicked'; } return 'not found'; }","kind":"evaluate"},"target":"host","targetId":"A3CC7B291135C391245C2E310AEEE34D"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":139908,"output":533,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140441,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772466303294}}
