{"type":"message","id":"97e75678","parentId":"b015eeba","timestamp":"2026-03-02T15:55:37.379Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我回复藏月亮的兔子🐰，她是我们的朋友，外号 wjj。我需要在通知页面找到她的评论并回复。\n\n之前 snapshot 里看到她的评论是\"此帖不错\"，在通知列表里。让我回通知页面找她。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"懂了，去回复 wjj！回通知页面：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_62a6ec1881bd45bbaefdc1f0","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"navigate","profile":"openclaw","target":"host","targetId":"A3CC7B291135C391245C2E310AEEE34D","url":"https://www.xiaohongshu.com/notification"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":171780,"output":242,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":172022,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772466914282}}
